About Us
Meet Michael LaVallee and Michael Fiorenza.
These 2 Owners/Founders have gone above and beyond to make this bar great!
Bringing their nightlife and industry experience back from Las Vegas, NV. where both worked in some of the biggest nightclubs in the world; before moving back to Fort Lauderdale to pursue their dreams of Owning their own bar!
Michael Fiorenza is a Fort Lauderdale Local, Born and Raised here and attended Cardinal Gibbons HS!
Michael LaVallee is from Concord, NH. However LaVallee has considered Fort Lauderdale his home for many years of his life.
